====READ ME=====
----------------

Please use Python 3.6 environment to run the programs.
Dependencies are numpy and cv2 modules for Python.
Image file used is actual.png in the same directory.
The source file for Q1 is A1Q1.py and that for Q2 is A1Q2.py.

To get results of Q1 and Q2, please run:
$ python3 A1Q1.py
$ python3 A1Q2.py
in terminal, respectively.

Result Images folder has all resulting images of the program.
Assignment1.pdf is the report.
sample.jpg is used for testing all codes (after being grayscaled and resized).
